rdfstar.Q3: prefix wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> prefix wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> SELECT (COUNT (?discardedArtist) as ?num)  ?discardedArtist WHERE { ?artwork wdt:P31 ?type. ?type (wdt:P279*) wd:Q838948. {BIND(<< ?artwork wdt:P170 ?discardedArtist >> AS ?discardedAttribution)} UNION {BIND(<< ?artwork wdt:P50 ?discardedArtist >> AS ?discardedAttribution)} FILTER NOT EXISTS {?artwork wdt:P170|wdt:P50 ?discardedArtist} } GROUP BY ?discardedArtist ORDER BY DESC (?num)
